The Music app keeps freezing. I used to think it was because of my phone, even though no other apps had issues. But after changing my phone, I realized the problem is entirely with the app. I was one of the last 3-4 people still resisting Spotify, but I guess I’ll have to switch once my subscription ends. Edit: I'm back 😃 I didn't like how the other app's algorithm works, its discovery and recommendations. YouTube Music also seems to have fixed the freezing issue. I'm impressed.
